  <main>
    <h3>Welcome to this holy place</h3>
    <span>Here I work and pray to my coding god whose name is null</span>
    <span>Some of my projects are:</span>

    <div>
      <li>
        <a href="https://sparrxw.netlify.app/" target="_blank">Portfolio Website</a> - Full-stack portfolio
        site made using React and Sanity
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://restaurant-landingpage.web.app/" target="_blank">Gericht Restaurant Landing Page</a> - Front-end
        project made using React and sass
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://modern-ui-project.web.app/" target="_blank">OpenGPT 3 Landing page</a> - Front-end project
